universe u

constant obj : Type u

constant Cow : obj
constant Lion : obj
constant Squirrel : obj
constant Tiger : obj

constant Big : obj → Prop
constant Green : obj → Prop
constant Eats : obj → obj → Prop
constant Sees : obj → obj → Prop
constant Visits : obj → obj → Prop
constant Round : obj → Prop
constant Nice : obj → Prop
constant Kind : obj → Prop

axiom T1 : ¬ Big Cow
axiom T2 : ¬ Green Cow
axiom T3 : Eats Lion Tiger
axiom T4 : Sees Lion Cow
axiom T5 : Visits Lion Cow
axiom T6 : ¬ Visits Lion Squirrel
axiom T7 : Visits Lion Tiger
axiom T8 : Big Squirrel
axiom T9 : Round Squirrel
axiom T10 : ¬ Green Tiger
axiom T11 : ¬ Sees Tiger Cow

axiom R1 : ∀ x : obj, Sees x Squirrel ∧ Eats Squirrel Cow → Round Cow
axiom R2 : ∀ x : obj, Green x → Eats x Tiger
axiom R3 : ∀ x : obj, Round Squirrel → Visits Squirrel Cow
axiom R4 : ∀ x : obj, Eats x Cow → Sees x Squirrel
axiom R5 : ∀ x : obj, Sees x Tiger ∧ Visits Tiger Squirrel → Nice x
axiom R6 : ∀ x : obj, Round x → Eats x Cow
axiom R7 : ∀ x : obj, Kind x → Eats x Cow
axiom R8 : ∀ x : obj, Visits Tiger Cow → Sees Cow Squirrel
axiom R9 : ∀ x : obj, Sees x Cow → Eats Cow Tiger

theorem cow_sees_squirrel : Sees Cow Squirrel :=
begin
  apply R8,
  exact T5,
end

-- The answer is True
